    border-radius: 5px;
    line-height: 1.6;"><p>/imagine prompt: On a summer night, high up in the mountains, there is a vast grassy plain in the distance. The sky is filled with countless stars, with no moon in sight. The scene is rendered in a 3D style, with intricate details and realistic textures that bring the landscape to life. --ar 16:9 --v 5</p>
<p>/imagine prompt: In the darkness of a summer night, atop a mountain, lies a sprawling grassy meadow that extends as far as the eye can see. In the distance, a range of mountains adds to the grandeur of the scene. The sky above is adorned with a mesmerizing display of stars, their brilliance illuminating the landscape. The absence of the moon intensifies the depth of the night. The image is presented in a 3D format, capturing the intricate details of the terrain and the celestial beauty above. --ar 16:9 --v 5</p>
<p>/imagine prompt: As the sun sets on a summer evening, revealing a star-studded night sky, you find yourself standing on a mountain peak covered in lush green grass. In the distance, there is a vast expanse of grassland, stretching towards a range of majestic mountains. The sky above is devoid of any moonlight, allowing the stars to shine with unrivaled brilliance. The image is rendered in a 3D style, emphasizing the depth and scale of the landscape. --ar 16:9 --v 5</p>
<p>/imagine prompt: On a warm summer night, high up on a mountain, lies a picturesque scene. A wide grassy plain stretches across the horizon, leading up to a range of towering mountains in the distance. Above, the night sky is ablaze with an array of twinkling stars, their light casting a magical glow on the landscape. There is no moon in sight, intensifying the darkness and adding an air of mystery to the scene. The image is depicted in a 3D style, bringing a sense of depth and realism to the composition. --ar 16:9 --v 5</p></div>

