<p>Sayori: “We’re here for you, we’ll support you no matter what.”</p>
<p>Natsuki: “You’ve got this, Yuri. We believe in you.”</p>
<p>(With the help of her friends and the medical team, Yuri successfully gives birth to a healthy baby. The girls stay by her side in the hospital, cheering her up and helping her recover.)</p>
<p>Yuri: (tearfully holding her newborn baby) “Thank you, everyone. I couldn’t have done it without you all.”</p>
<p>Monika: “We’re so proud of you, Yuri. You’re an amazing mother.”</p>
<p>Sayori: “And we’re so happy to welcome the newest member of our literature club family.”</p>
<p>Natsuki: “Yeah, now we have another little bookworm to join our discussions.”</p>
<p>(The girls share a heartwarming moment as they welcome the newest addition to their club. Despite the unexpected turn of events, their friendship and support for each other only grows stronger.)</p></div>

